“If there is anything the government should learn from this flood, it is to
take education and women empowerment more seriously,”
[reports](http://teeth.com.pk/blog/2010/08/25/pakistan-flood-relief-field-
notes-from-doctors-to-sukkur-%E2%80%93-day-2) _Dr. Syed Nabeel Zafar_ in a
medical field note from Sukkur in Sindh province of Pakistan.

